OL,3,CWhat is a 'thundery breakdown' and why
OL,4,Cdo we get it after hot weather?
OL,6,FLightning in Belfast sets off solar
OL,7,Flights in a front garden on Wednesday
OL,8,Fnight (Video: Sharon Ross)
OL,10,FAfter record-breaking temperatures
OL,11,Fthis week, brace yourself for a
OL,12,Fdramatic end to the current hot spell
OL,13,Fas thunderstorms move in.
OL,15,FWhat is a 'thundery breakdown'?
OL,17,FThe term 'thundery breakdown' is a
OL,18,Fcolloquialism used by the media to
OL,19,Fdescribe the common occurrence of
OL,20,Fthunderstorms following a spell of
OL,21,Fhot, dry, settled weather.
