OL,3,CWhat is a 'thundery breakdown' and why
OL,4,Cdo we get it after hot weather?
OL,6,FWhy does it happen?
OL,8,FThunderstorms are essentially giant
OL,9,Fshowers.
OL,11,FContrary to popular belief, a shower
OL,12,Fis not a light outbreak of rain (in
OL,13,Ffact, some showers can actually
OL,14,Fproduce a month's worth of rain in
OL,15,Fjust a few hours!).
