OL,3,CWhat is a 'thundery breakdown' and why
OL,4,Cdo we get it after hot weather?
OL,6,FThe haphazard nature of the way that
OL,7,Fshowers and thunderstorms form makes
OL,8,Fthem hard to pin down, but it's likely
OL,9,Fthat eastern parts of Northern
OL,10,FIreland, Dartmoor, Cornwall, Wales and
OL,11,Fthe Midlands will be the most likely
OL,12,Fspots.
